# Unsaved Changes Pattern

When a page can have unsaved changes and the user attempts to navigate away from it, the following must be implemented:
- **ALWAYS** add the `projects/shared-ui/src/lib/core/unsaved-changes-guard` guard to the route.
- **ALWAYS** implement the `UnsavedChangesAware` type from `projects/shared-ui/src/lib/core/unsaved-changes-guard` on the component.
